      }}>{`React Hooks`}</a>{` yet and those technical explanations mean nothing to you, don't worry we're going to slowly walk through this.  With illustrations. Because  who the fork properly understands `}<em parentName="p">{`"side effects"`}</em>{`?`}</p>
